    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tinker Pilot is a VR spaceflight simulator built from the ground up for <strong>maximum sense of presence</strong>. Operate a fully interactable and customizable cockpit and take full control of your ship in a sci-fi open environment. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Exhaustive Ship Systems</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every ship system is designed as an <strong>interface</strong> with a series of actions and data that can be accessed from your cockpit. Take full control over every thruster, sensor, stabilizer or any ship component and <strong>make your piloting as complex as you like</strong>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1257710/extras/0c4450c4c6b45451d8bc1907769b9854.poster.avif?t=1772123166\" width=614 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1257710/extras/0c4450c4c6b45451d8bc1907769b9854.webm?t=1772123166\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1257710/extras/0c4450c4c6b45451d8bc1907769b9854.mp4?t=1772123166\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >1:1 Philosophy</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tinker Pilot has been designed with 1:1 immersion at its core to achieve the <strong>maximum sense of presence</strong> you can get. <strong>Use any combination of input methods</strong> (HOTAS, VR motion controllers, hand tracking, etc.) and your spaceship cockpit will be adapted to ensure there's no mismatch between what you <i>see</i> and what you <i>feel</i>.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1257710/extras/490741b534d5b17c5a7b07143f626451.poster.avif?t=1772123166\" width=614 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1257710/extras/490741b534d5b17c5a7b07143f626451.webm?t=1772123166\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1257710/extras/490741b534d5b17c5a7b07143f626451.mp4?t=1772123166\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Cockpit customization</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whether you want a layout that adapts to your piloting style, a virtual representation of your real devices or just some decoration, the <strong>in-game cockpit editor</strong> has you covered. <strong>Place, scale and animate any cockpit element</strong> to your liking and <strong>import your own models</strong> so that they are integrated into the game. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1257710/extras/78a6b9008394a8c6997641ed9798e3e5.poster.avif?t=1772123166\" width=614 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1257710/extras/78a6b9008394a8c6997641ed9798e3e5.webm?t=1772123166\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1257710/extras/78a6b9008394a8c6997641ed9798e3e5.mp4?t=1772123166\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Engaging Gameplay</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The gameplay in Tinker Pilot is meant to be diverse and challenging, but above all is <strong>meant to be fun</strong>. Complete different missions and challenges in a <strong>realistic physics</strong> environment where the proximity to terrain, stations, ships, and other objects gives a <strong>greater sense of movement and speed</strong>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1257710/extras/2f152d152e430eadd49928ae8c1d7845.poster.avif?t=1772123166\" width=614 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1257710/extras/2f152d152e430eadd49928ae8c1d7845.webm?t=1772123166\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1257710/extras/2f152d152e430eadd49928ae8c1d7845.mp4?t=1772123166\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
